- CREATE: `apps/gateway/src/api/schemas.ts`
- CREATE: `apps/gateway/src/api/generate-openapi.ts`
- CREATE: `apps/gateway/src/routes/openapi.ts`
- MODIFY: `apps/gateway/src/routes/index.ts` (add openapi route)
