## Acceptance Criteria

1. All notification event types trigger appropriate notifications
2. In-app notifications appear in real-time via WebSocket
3. Email notifications are delivered within 30 seconds (non-digest)
4. Slack integration works with workspace OAuth flow
5. Webhook delivery includes retry logic (3 attempts with exponential backoff)
6. User preferences are respected for all notification routing
7. Quiet hours prevent non-urgent notifications during specified times
8. Daily/weekly digests are delivered at user-configured times
9. Notification center shows unread badge with accurate count
10. Mark as read/unread works individually and in bulk
11. Notification search and filtering works across all fields
12. Test notification feature works for all channels
13. Performance: Dispatch 1000 notifications/second without blocking

## Testing Strategy

- Unit tests for notification service and each channel
- Integration tests for end-to-end delivery
- Mock external services (SendGrid, Slack) in tests
- Load testing for high-volume scenarios
- E2E tests for notification preferences UI

